## Replacing iDRAC/iLO/IPMI

| Feature | iDRAC | AIdrac |
|---------|-------|--------|
| Network Required | Yes | No |
| License Cost | $$$ | Free |
| Protocols | Proprietary | Open |
| AI Integration | No | Native |
| Physical Audit | No | Braille punchcard |
| Phone Control | No | DTMF |
| Ultrasonic | No | Yes |

